    MC "Yeah, I-"
    MCT "Wait, what?"
    MC "Really?"
    show AE neutral-annoyed
    AE "I wouldn't answer that I am if I wasn't. I already had at least somewhat of an inkling of what the school was for, even before the announcement."
    MCT "She did?"
    MC "I kind of thought that-"
